%N A183633 Number of (n+1) X (n+1) 0..3 arrays with every 2 X 2 subblock summing to 6.
%H A183633 Christian Krause, <a href="/A183633/a183633.txt">Proof of formula</a>, Jun 19 2026
%H A183633 <a href="/index/Rec#order_04">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (10,-35,50,-24).
%F A183633 a(n) = 4*(2^n-1)*3^(n+1)+4*2^n = 12*6^n-12*3^n+4*2^n. - _Zhuorui He_, Jun 13 2026
